<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="216" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,1679,2038]" pageId="15" pageNumber="216">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,1746,1771]" pageId="15" pageNumber="216">Comments.</emphasis>
The species has not been recorded since its description, except a single record from the Ivory Coast by 
<bibRefCitation author="Poisson" box="[256,429,1780,1805]" pageId="15" pageNumber="216" refString="Poisson, R. A. (1968) Contributions a la connaissance de la faune entomologique de la Cote d'Ivoire (J. Decelle 1961 - 1964). Annales du Musee du Congo Belge, Tervuren, in- 8 °, Zoologie, 165, 399 - 403." type="journal article" year="1968">Poisson (1968)</bibRefCitation>
. However, the latter record requires confirmation. The subspecific status of this taxon and its relationship with 
<taxonomicName box="[380,596,1813,1838]" class="Insecta" family="Hebridae" genus="Hebrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="216" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="pusillus" subSpecies="pusillus">
<emphasis box="[380,596,1813,1838]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="216">H. pusillus pusillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
requires re-examination.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,1679,2038]" pageId="15" pageNumber="216">
In the MZHF are 9 specimens from the type locality: ‘holotype nr. 11635, 3 spec. on the same pin, no locality label, determination handwritten label by Poisson, no year; allotype nr. 11636, 1 spec., Santo Antão: Pombas, 23.– 
<date box="[151,280,1913,1938]" pageId="15" pageNumber="216" value="1953-12-25">25.12.1953</date>
, Lindberg, + Poisson determination label in 1956; paratype nr. 11637, 2 spec. on the same pin, Santo Antão: Pombas, 23.– 
<date box="[382,514,1946,1971]" pageId="15" pageNumber="216" value="1953-12-25">25.12.1953</date>
, Lindberg, + Poisson determination label in 1956; paratype (red label no number), 3 spec. on two pins, Santo Antão: Pombas, 23.– 
<date box="[688,820,1980,2005]" pageId="15" pageNumber="216" value="1953-12-25">25.12.1953</date>
, Lindberg, + Poisson determination label in 1956.’ (L. Huldén, pers. comm.).
</paragraph>
